  "description": {
    "en": "Herbal preparation derived from Tianma. Tianma is made from Gastrodia elatae, an unusual type of orchid that grows on a fungus. It is a sweet tasting, neutral herb that enters the liver meridian. It is used to expel wind, to stop spasms and..."
